          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Some of the largest companies are now using brain scans to study how we react neurologically to certain foods, especially to sugar. They've discovered that the brain lights up for sugar the same way it does for cocaine.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
